<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="disagreement-n">disagreement <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ˌdɪsə'ɡriːmənt/    美 /ˌdɪsə'ɡriːmənt/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-c-u">1.★ <strong>[C] &amp; [U] 分歧；争论；不一致：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We’ve <strong>had</strong> a few <strong>disagreements</strong>, but we’re still good friends.
虽然有过一些分歧，但我们仍是好朋友。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>There were <strong>disagreements among</strong> doctors <strong>about</strong> the best way to treat the disease. 
对治疗这种疾病的最佳方案医生们意见不一。</p></div></div>